reviewText: Any Thomas the tank book is a hit to m,y 3 yr old grandson, they all have a moral to the story a  great way to encourage reading, quiet time, and time for bonding with parents and grandparents

These are five episodes in one DVD. The best thing here is that, it's related to the movie "Tale of the Brave" where you can see the new characters Marion and Timothy having new stories. in general, it was a very nice addition for my son who is now learning friendship, courage, and other nice things from Thomas and his friends.
Can't go wrong with a Thomas movie!!

This DVD contains five episodes from the Thomas & Friends cartoon. Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. Signals Crossed
2. Marion and the Pipe
3. No Steam Without Coal
4. Duncan and the Grumpy Passenger
5. Thomas and the Emergency Cable

Bonus Features
1. Roll Call Song Music Video
2. Searching Everywhere Music Video
3. Guess Who? Puzzles
Another great video for the Thomas lovers.
We love Thomas & Friends! And we love that the newer episodes focus more on the other characters besides Thomas -- or Cheeky as my son calls him. It's a cute episode. Glad we bought it!
It was enjoyed very much by our 3yr old grandson.  It tells a good story
My son loves this show! Loves Thomas and Friends of course.......but the chorus singing is amazing, special effects, and themes are always great and educational.
